{{Otheruses|Plot}}
'''Plot''' was a hero in the mythology of the [[Sentience/Legends|sentient]] [[Bothan/Legends|Bothan]] [[Species/Legends|species]]. The Bothans used their name as a family name.<ref name="GCG">''[[Galactic Campaign Guide]]''</ref>

==Behind the scenes==
Plot was mentioned in the ''[[Galactic Campaign Guide]]'', a supplement for the ''[[Star Wars Roleplaying Game]]'' that was written by [[Peter M. Schweighofer|Peter Schweighofer]] and [[J.D. Wiker]] and published by [[Wizards of the Coast]] in [[2003]].<ref name="GCG" />

